casebody.data:
November 20, 1970

No. —.

Citizens to Preserve Overton Park, Inc., et al. v. Volpe, Secretary, Department of Transportation, et al.

C. A. 6th Cir. Application for stay presented to Mr. Justice Stewart, and by him referred to the Court, set for argument on Monday, December 7. Typewritten briefs shall be filed by Thursday, December 3.
